                                <h3>Our Mission</h3>
                                <p class="mx-3">The FoodShare Map helps connect people who are food insecure with food resources. It identifies socially conscious people and organizations who have excess food and wish to avoid wasting this food. This information is made available so that those in need of food can more easily locate these resources.</p>

                                <p class="mx-3" >The service is community based. It is welcoming to all in need and grateful to those who wish to help. It is devoted to respectfully assisting those who are experiencing challenges in their lives. </p>
